## Grant Deliverables
- We received funding in OceanDAO [Round 2](https://port.oceanprotocol.com/t/oceandao-r2-proposal-rugpullindex-com/364), [Round 3](https://port.oceanprotocol.com/t/rugpullindex-com-round-3-proposal/434) and [Round 4](https://port.oceanprotocol.com/t/rugpullindex-com-round-3-proposal/434).
- For more reliable runway projections, we convert most of our OCEAN incomes from the OceanDAO into USDC: [R2](https://etherscan.io/tx/0xc812e21a949313b97c240fbf96315e18df7599f5ff1606ce4109d1bc585ac6bf), [R3](https://etherscan.io/tx/0xe34d8ad69db282b51fca2459591bc47e46e69edddfbd5c129bebe8a880f1f860), [R4 1](https://etherscan.io/tx/0x50536d2b103e1bdfaccac12a159171b21c795402dc58329bafbee624bcc038bd).
- Since the project’s beginning, our [blog 1](https://rugpullindex.com/blog) has been updated frequently to show the project’s progress. In April, we’ve:
    - Improved the TOP 25 ranking by adding additional data ([blog post](https://rugpullindex.com/blog#April262021)).
    - Improved the page’s download speed ([blog post](https://rugpullindex.com/blog#MajorPerformanceImprovementisLive)).
    - Improved the crawler’s reliability ([blog post](https://rugpullindex.com/blog#RecentUpdates)).
